high_descs: Move down the hall then forward to the green chair with the two newspapers on it
Pick up the newspaper to the left on the chair
Carry the newspaper to the corner floor lamp on the left
anns.task_desc: Carry a newspaper while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then take a step to your left then walk to the small table then take a step to your left and walk until you are even with a green chair with two papers on it and turn left and walk to it when you are.
Pick up the paper on the right.
Turn right and walk to the black table then turn left and walk to the light.
Look up at the light then turn it on.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a newspaper by lamp light.

high_descs: Turn left to make your way around the coffee table to the farthest armchair in the room.
Pick up the newspaper on the right on the armchair seat.
Turn to face the tall lamp on the right of the armchair.
anns.task_desc: Look at a newspaper by the light of a tall lamp.
